{"tid":481551,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我好想定實曬個心係依家個另一半度","createTime":"2017-11-27T09:50:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-27T12:54:19.000Z","uid":142098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4ea576ebd884a8d0a8c14e21d82edeccfb3a13a3","tid":481551,"uid":142098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T09:50:19.000Z","msg":"我好愛另一半 但係我見到靚女或者長腿大波 都會心郁郁 有時係到問自己如果有女送上門我會唔會食 我個心會好易動搖 我知我好貪心 所以我唔想再係咁 求巴絲意見 我好想對另一半專一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347cf6ce0ac04dcc481a98f238e0a0cb4a03927e","tid":481551,"uid":28614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T09:53:00.000Z","msg":"如果你食左，你就永遠失去你另一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1534e16fcd429c49e2b3f52ea6161bfe2e20a469","tid":481551,"uid":96,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T09:54:44.000Z","msg":"唔會有女送上門俾你食 唔洗擔心"},{"pid":"0bd8fc5a47c1b268f0f54fbf9a09f7203ae1e3de","tid":481551,"uid":22566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T09:56:11.000Z","msg":"你係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">想</span>好愛佢啫"},{"pid":"068d56671d6b1e06e9e4f52772cfe8a62a1bcd86","tid":481551,"uid":85243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T10:09:49.000Z","msg":"其實真係送到上門擺埋到咀邊 有幾多人真係會say no?<br />\n我會話你諗多左多過係唔專一<br />\n如果閣下係靚仔多女埋身既話應該都閱女無數<br />\n送上門做到咁cheap既九成都唔高質得去邊再唔係就有企圖<br />\n諗一諗你食完有咩後果 你以後對住另一半都唔可以坦誠放鬆 有d良知或者真係愛佢既應該可以自制"},{"pid":"8f387730af82a4536de6c3ee97cfeb0c66c13dd5","tid":481551,"uid":142098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T12:53:10.000Z","msg":"但係真係送到你門口 我就唔會諗咁多後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b506e240d8dd2707af9a139dea1beca3fc827c","tid":481551,"uid":142098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T12:54:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔會有女送上門俾你食 唔洗擔心</blockquote><br />\n他有 但唔高質冇食 但我諗高質既會食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我覺得自己好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3126ee6b5789ead3a39da49de09def0cde1ae730","tid":481551,"uid":142098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T12:54:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔會有女送上門俾你食 唔洗擔心</blockquote><br />\n他有 但唔高質冇食 但我諗高質既會食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我覺得自己好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係有"}]}